00:17:56,303 --> 00:17:59,080
♫ <i> Tears turn into heavy rain </i> ♫

223
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:03,520
♫ <i> We went back to when we first met </i> ♫

224
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:08,260
♫ <i> I immediately saw your charming face </i> ♫

225
