00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:21,606
Who brought her here? Speak!

248
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,900
A couple of officers.

249
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:26,148
What did they look like?

250
00:19:26,148 --> 00:19:28,740
